{subhead}Inga Gaming Developer System{def}
{left}
{pp}
Computer City have announced that they will port the Inga gaming system to the Amiga
for AmigaOS 4 and Amiga Anywhere (DE) which will allow gamers to design and develop their
own adventures in a friendly developer package.
{pp}
Inga can write graphics adventure games such as Monkey Island and it features user-
friendly tools and a flexible and powerful script language. 
{pp}
Inga is currently used to develop a game called Ermentrud.
{pp}
